Package util.properties

Class Summary
PropertiesHandler A middleman that loads parsed property values into an object, or stores the values of the object into a .properties file format.

Annotation Types Summary
Property Apply this annotation to fields which you need to load from or store into .properties files.
PropertyGetter Apply this annotation to any method which act as a getter (accessor) for a property.
PropertySetter Apply this annotation to any method which act as a setter (mutator) for a property.
